{"id":437496,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/05/【立此存照】获两千万次播放后-4分多钟雷洋案调查/","date":"2016-05-11T06:34:39Z","modified":"2016-05-11T15:28:32Z","title":"【立此存照】获两千万次播放后 4分多钟雷洋案调查视频被掉包","content":"<p>腾讯新闻“焦点·现场”节目于中国时间2016年5月11日发布了一则题为《雷洋涉嫖身亡事件：目击者拍摄执法现场曝光》的视频，<strong>其中有网民拍摄的雷洋被抓时求助的画面，还有腾讯记者采访现场目击者的内容，时长4分多钟</strong>。遭到替换前已有一千多条评论和超两千万的播放量。</p>\n<p>数小时后，腾讯移花接木，将原始链接下的视频内容替换成只有12秒且画面模糊、无任何讲解的现场视频，评论被删至仅剩16条，但保留了两千多万的播放量。</p>\n<p>不久后，原链接内容再次被换，目前为北京电视台报道该案的新闻片段。这则标题为《“雷洋案”足疗女露面受访》的报道中，一名“足疗女”身穿看守所的衣服在摄像机前接受采访，称雷洋前去足疗时“帮他打了飞机”。</p>\n<p>中国数字时代已将4分多钟的原始视频内容上传至<strong>YouTube备份</strong>（<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tXbTFvYJhUA\" target=\"_blank\">地址</a>）：</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tXbTFvYJhUA\" width=\"500\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>4分钟版原始视频截图：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-437521\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-437521\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图1.jpg\" alt=\"雷洋报道原视频截图1\" width=\"500\" height=\"283\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图1.jpg 1698w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图1-300x170.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图1-768x435.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图1-1024x580.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图2.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-437520\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-437520\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图2.jpg\" alt=\"雷洋报道原视频截图2\" width=\"500\" height=\"283\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图2.jpg 1692w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图2-300x170.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图2-768x434.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图2-1024x579.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图3.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-437519\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-437519\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图3.jpg\" alt=\"雷洋报道原视频截图3\" width=\"500\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图3.jpg 1692w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图3-300x170.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图3-768x436.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/雷洋报道原视频截图3-1024x581.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>原视频页面截图</strong>（<a href=\"http://v.qq.com/cover/p/pevi81lpi14li4l.html\" target=\"_blank\">链接</a>），<strong>此时已无法观看，简介内容也已被清空。</strong>但评论仍显示为1240条：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-437517\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-437517\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换1.jpg\" alt=\"视频替换1\" width=\"550\" height=\"538\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换1.jpg 1682w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换1-300x294.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换1-768x752.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换1-1024x1002.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换1-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>从原始视频热门评论截图中可以看出，多数网民对“足疗嫖娼”的说法并不买账：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/原视频评论-1.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-437518\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-437518\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/原视频评论-1.png\" alt=\"原视频评论\" width=\"500\" height=\"817\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/原视频评论-1.png 1254w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/原视频评论-1-184x300.png 184w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/原视频评论-1-768x1254.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/原视频评论-1-627x1024.png 627w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>原内容遭第一次替换后变成仅剩12秒且画面模糊、无任何讲解的视频，评论数被删至16条：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-437516\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-437516\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换.jpg\" alt=\"视频替换\" width=\"550\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换.jpg 1676w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换-300x290.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换-768x742.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/视频替换-1024x990.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>截至发稿时，<strong>原视频已再次遭到替换</strong>，目前为转发北京电视台新闻节目。评论内容被清零，但还是保留了两千多万的播放量：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/替换3.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-437515\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-437515\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/替换3.jpg\" alt=\"替换3\" width=\"550\" height=\"524\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/替换3.jpg 1684w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/替换3-300x286.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/替换3-768x732.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/替换3-1024x975.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>姓党的<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/05/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e8%bf%99%e5%b1%8a%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95%e8%ae%b0%e5%bd%95%e4%bb%aa%e6%9c%89%e5%85%9a%e6%80%a7%ef%bc%8c%e8%ae%a9%e5%ae%83%e5%9d%8f%e5%b0%b1%e5%9d%8f/\" target=\"_blank\">不只是执法记录仪</a>。</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,13770],"tags":[12714,30319,17389,9006,8616,9421,31012]}